plot: Kris and Kim arrive in Vienna where they experience racism. Kourtney wants the moving date to their new house to be as delayed as it can be.

Kris, Kim and North head to Vienna as the guests of honor for the annual Opera Ball. But their fairytale trip quickly turns into a nightmare when Kris is robbed of all her favorite items and Kim is the victim of multiple racist remarks. Will she be able to keep her cool? Back in the States, Kourtney and Scott move into the mansion of their dreams! But that too comes with a few unexpected surprises. See the drama go down!—Anonymous
